Titolo: Crystal Warriors

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Crystal Warriors (アーリエル クリスタル伝説, Ariel: Crystal Densetsu, "Ariel: Crystal Legend") is a turn-based strategy video game developed and published by Sega for the Game Gear in Japan in 1991 and in Europe and North America in 1992. It was re-released for Virtual Console in 2013. A Japan-only sequel Royal Stone was published in 1995.

Genere: Strategy 

Valutazione: N/A
